26 (f) Arepresentativeofthedivisionofeconomicdevelopment,appointedbythecommissioner
27 ofthedepartmentofbusinessandeconomicaffairs.
28 (g) ArepresentativeoftheuniversitysystemofNewHampshire,appointedbythechancellor.
29 (h) Twopublicmembers,appointedbythegovernor.
30 IV. Thecouncilshallelectachairperson,whosedutiesshallincludecallingmeetings.
